plot: Susan Strong and her allies infiltrate the mysterious Super Porp factory.

Its the day of the month everyone loves. Super Porp Day (grape soda in a can). Fin, Jake, BMO and Marcy are skating and waiting at the local Squeez-E-Mart for the vending machine to be refilled with the grape soda. They begin to wonder where Super Porp comes from when Marcy says shes been drinking it since she was a little girl. Should they chase down the answer or just enjoy the soda. The refill-bots fly off and go under ground, to Susan Strongs homeland. Where suddenly a crime takes place. Susan will discover the truth!—mrwarcriminal
